Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.86,0:00:06.83,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Cheerilee is sweet and kind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.31,0:00:10.58,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,She's the best teacher we could hope for
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.94,0:00:14.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The perfect stallion you and I must find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.48,0:00:20.98,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,One to really make her heart so-oar
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.34,0:00:23.64,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But... This one's too young
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.07,0:00:25.70,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,This one's too old
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.49,0:00:29.63,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,He clearly has a terrible cold
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.36,0:00:31.51,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,This guy's too silly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.81,0:00:33.38,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,He's way too uptight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.65,0:00:36.47,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Well nothing's wrong with this one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.59,0:00:39.31,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,He seems alright
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.43,0:00:41.24,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,His girlfriend sure thinks so.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.24,0:00:42.15,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,How 'bout this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.39,0:00:44.09,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,He's much too flashy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.06,0:00:45.90,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,He might do
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.02,0:00:48.26,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,If he weren'tso splashy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.11,0:00:50.80,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Too short,too tall
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.04,0:00:52.86,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Too clean,too smelly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.98,0:00:58.42,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,He's strangely obsessed with tubs of jelly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.54,0:00:59.51,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,*sigh*
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.06,0:01:02.96,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I don't think that we're mistaken
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.50,0:01:07.01,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It seems all the good ones are taken
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.62,0:01:09.43,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I really feel that at this rate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.55,0:01:11.31,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We'll never find the perfect date
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.49,0:01:13.42,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Don't wanna quit and give up hope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.79,0:01:14.81,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Doing anything special
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.87,0:01:16.02,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For Hearts and Hooves Day?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.27,0:01:18.20,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Ohplease oh please oh please say
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.32,0:01:18.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:22.92,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We did it girls, we've found the one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.83,0:01:27.34,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Who will send our teacher's heart aflutter
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.88,0:01:29.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, let me get this straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.75,0:01:31.45,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Are you talkin' 'bout my brother?